Key points:

Uses async pipe everywhere for reactive subscriptions.

Shows loading, error, and empty states automatically.

Refresh button triggers the service to reload users.

4. Benefits of BehaviorSubject Approach

Centralized state: Users, loading, and error state live in service.

Reactive & clean components: Components just bind Observables.

Error handling: Automatic and centralized.

Supports multiple components: Any component can subscribe to the same users$.

Easy refresh: Just call refreshUsers() from anywhere.